In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Brenda Joyce COUNCIL. No. D-2816. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 3, 2014.

Opinion

Brenda Joyce Council, of Omaha, Nebraska, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring her to show cause why she should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
